videos.headline: Bennett finds an opening for short Georgia TD
videos.description: Stetson Bennett runs around the defenders and finds a clear path to the end zone for a 2-yard Georgia touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Bennett finds an opening for short Georgia TD) 2020/10/31 ESHEET

videos.headline: Georgia's White takes off for 22-yard TD run
videos.description: Zamir White runs into traffic, but breaks through and goes straight into the end zone for a 22-yard Bulldogs touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Georgia's White takes off for 22-yard TD run) 2020/10/31 ESHEET
